      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON RULER (5) boasts a strong record this course with 10 wins and six minors from 23 tries. Recorded a 1.5 lengths win (34.77) in a Mix 4/54/6 last time at this track. With a clean break looks hard to beat. WEST ON MODEL (6) skirted wide from an outside draw and found the front, leading until late when second (42.34) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 715m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Ready to find winning form. SAND FIRE (1) placed three back at this track then out of the placings last couple but moves to box 1 this time where she has performed well. Has the ability and expected to do much better. FLAWS AND SINS (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
